29:39.000 --> 29:41.208
It's complicated, but..

29:41.208 --> 29:43.291
I'm in love with a guy
who moved without telling me

29:43.291 --> 29:46.667
and I'll probably
never see him again.

29:47.625 --> 29:50.209
Who knows? Maybe you will.

29:50.209 --> 29:52.458
Another mystery.

29:52.458 --> 29:54.375
I guess so.

29:58.458 --> 30:00.458
[indistinct chattering]

